{"tid":2108644,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句，中學未試過蝦啲內向毒撚嘅話唔好話自己讀過書","createTime":"2020-07-14T16:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:20:38.000Z","uid":211802,"like":22,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7a45460e43c2b42e96fe7df1539cb2aa802e2c2e","tid":2108644,"uid":211802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"作為一個世界仔，喺呢個弱肉強食嘅世界裏面，識玩就一定係要蝦鳩啲內向毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ngroup project，學校旅行，Christmas party等等嘅嘢唔侵毒撚，或者當毒撚透明呢啲基本玩法我就唔講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講到蝦鳩毒撚最正嘅玩法，我之前有個po有講，就係問毒撚想唔想影相，等毒撚答ok之後就話「但我唔想同你影wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」，個毒撚就會呆撚咗喺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算唔係世界仔都應該要蝦鳩啲內向毒撚，我識得有隻內向毒撚，佢識得一個唔係好多fd嘅女仔，女仔同佢表面上幾fd<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一日個女仔為咗R班上面其他女仔做fd，將隻毒撚以前同fd講笑嗰陣時講嘅mean嘢當做真心說話咁講撚哂俾全世界知，全世界突然之間都唔撚爽隻毒撚，毒撚嘅fd又唔算多，百口莫辯，只能夠無啦啦俾其他人針撚咗成年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻毒撚R撚哂頭都唔係好知發生咩事，直到佢grad咗好耐之後先feel到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係俾人撚到成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有次隻毒撚鍾意咗一個女仔，咁毒撚就走去搵蝦鳩佢嘅女仔問go唔go好(當時毒撚仲係俾人撚到一頭霧水，仲未知事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，條友就講到個女仔其實鍾意咗毒撚好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講到個女仔等緊毒撚主動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻毒撚又真係信，以為自己好撚有機，以為毒撚真係有得溝女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />結果俾人收皮仲俾人話恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我feel到個女仔都應該好迷，心諗做乜無啦啦有隻毒撚主動搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個世界就係咁，你唔蝦人，就會有人蝦你，毒撚們要怪就只能怪自己太毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nG持樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓主好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申:內向毒撚"},{"pid":"1e7f6c929ab499e4d6df0eef2b2dbc3cfa6b72ff","tid":2108644,"uid":148002,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77eKomM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77eKomM.png&h=e6f2d244&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"930bc82260e16f2f808e6a3975e06f400e08af57","tid":2108644,"uid":308264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"803515883457a6f08d10cb599808dc3dfcb7c8cb","tid":2108644,"uid":211802,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"930bc82260e16f2f808e6a3975e06f400e08af57","tid":2108644,"uid":308264,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:37:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19497060b13e4fc01348798d73e7c00efa46a9a7","tid":2108644,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1444810a368fd95c1a15620efa4cffa8820355c","tid":2108644,"uid":326758,"like":0,"dislike":